> The Twisted Halo at $1,955 with 197 reviews is the most validated setting in the entire white gold catalog. For lab pear buyers specifically, the F-color + Twisted Halo combination at under $3,400 is the most complete value I can show anyone in this category.
>
> One maintenance note I give every white gold buyer: schedule rhodium replating every 18 months. Don't wait until you see wear. Fresh rhodium on a white gold pear ring with a D–F stone is one of the best-looking things in fine jewelry at any price." — Farzana Hasan, **[Diamond Critics](https://diamondcritics.com/about-farzana/)**

